latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A mix of Clinique, Estée Lauder, Bobbi Brown, MAC and Smashbox products. 

Full product list:
Skin- Estee Lauder Advanced Night Repair, MAC Strobe cream, Bobbi brown Primer Plus Protection SPF50, Halo tinted moisturizer with Clinique buff brush, Clinique Even better all over Concealer + Eraser, Estee Lauder perfecting loose powder  powder, Bobbi brown Bronzing powder natural,, MAC Glowplay blush ‘Grand’, Estee Lauder highlight ‘Modern Mercery’, Fix + Magic radiance
Eyes- MAC Paintpot ‘Soft Ochre’, MAC eyeshadow ‘Stars and rockets’ and ‘Sushi flower’ + MAC brush 217 and 239, Clinique pretty easy eyelining pen and Clinique Lash power mascara
Lips- MAC Dervish lipliner, Clinique lipstick 02 Gauzy
